title: Tottenham 2 - Gent 2: Mauricio Pochettino’s men crash out Europa League
text:
Tottenham 2 - Gent 2: Mauricio Pochettino’s men crash out Europa League TOTTENHAM”S dreams of Europa League glory ended in front of a packed out Wembley stadium tonight. PUBLISHED: 21:58, Thu, Feb 23, 2017 | UPDATED: 22:00, Thu, Feb 23, 2017 
Mauricio Pochettino ’s men trailed Gent 1-0 going into the clash and looked to be on track to progress to the last-16 when Cristian Eriksen fired the hosts in front on 10 minutes. 
The winger took advantage of a mix up in the Gent defence by beating two defenders and slotting low past Lovre Kalinic. 
But Harry Kane’s own goal 10 minutes later saw Tottenham needing to score twice to advance.
